Please refer to our communication dated 9th May, 2024 regarding meeting of the Board of Directors to be held on Tuesday, 21st May, 2024, interalia, to approve the Audited Financial Results of BHEL for the quarter & year ended 31st March, 2024. In this respect and pursuant to Regulation 29 of the SEBI (Listing Obligations & Disclosure Requirements) Regulations, 2015, it is informed that recommendation of Final dividend, if any, for the Financial Year 2023-24 will also be considered by the Board in the aforesaid meeting.
